title: Lauryn Goodman reveals son Kairo's heart-wrenching reaction to England losing to Spain in the Euros 2024 final - as he begs to call father Kyle Walker

description: ROBERT HARDMAN: For a moment it seemed that England's last-minute merchants might just pull off another great escape, but Spain fired in a goal which dictated there would be no happy ending.
title: For 13 exquisite minutes, Three Lions fans dared to dream that England could win the Euros but now the long trudge back to Blighty begins, writes ROBERT HARDMAN

description: Two-thirds of people say they are very or somewhat worried about being told they have cancer, according to a new poll from the Cancer Research UK Cambridge Centre.
title: Cancer is biggest health concern among Brits - with late detection the largest worry, poll reveals

description: African babies are set to receive the R21 jab, a £3 malaria vaccine developed by a team at the University of Oxford that could potentially eradicate the disease within a decade.
title: Milestone in malaria battle as £3 vaccine is rolled out across Africa which could eradicate killer, mosquito-borne illness within 10 years

description: Doja Cat commanded attention as she sported a sexy Ginger Spice outfit while performing at Wireless Festival in London on Sunday night.
title: Doja Cat leaves little to the imagination in a Union Jack corset and lace thong as she performs in a ginger wig at Wireless Festival

description: Iris Law cheered on her rumoured England footballer boyfriend Trent Alexander-Arnold in Berlin as the Three Lions took on Spain in the Euros final on Sunday.
title: Iris Law cheers on 'boyfriend' Trent Alexander-Arnold in the stands after jetting to Berlin to support him for England's Euros final clash

description: Olly Murs held his head in his hands as he watched Spain defeat England 2-1 in the nail-biting Euro 2024 final on Sunday.
title: Olly Murs holds his head in his hands while gutted Rob Beckett makes a speedy departure out of Berlin as they lead the devastated stars following England's heartbreaking Euro loss

description: Zara McDermott and boyfriend Sam Thompson have unfollowed her Strictly Come Dancing partner Graziano Di Prima following him being sacked from the BBC show.
title: Zara McDermott and boyfriend Sam Thompson unfollow Strictly's Graziano Di Prima after he was accused of 'hitting and kicking her' in rehearsals

description: Phillip Schofield has shared his first selfie to Instagram in more than a year as he showed his support to the England football team in the Euro's 2024 final on Sunday.

description: Harry Styles showed his support to the England team as he watched the Euro's 2024 final against Spain on Sunday at the Olympiastadion stadium in Berlin, Germany.

description: The Three Lions were beaten 2-1 by Spain in Berlin on Sunday night despite a late comeback goal from Cole Palmer.
title: Gary Neville describes England's Euro defeat as a 'never ending story'

description: Fans of Shannen Doherty reacted to the news of her death from cancer on Saturday at the age of 53. Many recalled the on-screen romance of Shannen and Luke Perry on Beverly Hills 90210.
title: Shannen Doherty fans react to her breast cancer death years after her 90210 costar Luke Perry died from a stroke: 'Glad she's reunited with Luke'

description: England suffered an agonising 2-1 defeat at the Olympiastadion thanks to goals from Williams and Oyarzabal. The Real Sociedad forward pounced in the 86th minute.
title: Didi Hamann labels England's Euro 2024 campaign 'atrocious' and claims Gareth Southgate's side were responsible for SEVEN of the tournament's worst 10 matches
